IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User jethrokuan95@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass mbsync/jethrokuan95@gmail.com"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
# The trailing "/" is important
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/Inbox
SubFolders Legacy

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/All Mail" !*@*
Sync All

Create Both
SyncState *
